{"tid":866454,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］揀聖誕禮物","createTime":"2018-10-18T01:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T01:56:14.000Z","uid":155346,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2016991456cbd2ce24a38138ae01add2431b40","tid":866454,"uid":155346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:27:25.000Z","msg":"小弟個Hall自己個層係嚟緊星期日會交換聖誕禮物（無錯係早兩個月）<br />\n有人話就咁交換太普通，於是提議左以下遊戲規則：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/18/091311_71286a4aaa09a10d317eccfe956d9242.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F091311_71286a4aaa09a10d317eccfe956d9242.png&h=fe9fe727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概就係你唔會知份禮物最後會去咗邊個到，有可能係留返比自己。所以買伏野的話可能會伏到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依加煩緊揀咩好 想大家比下意見 筆直大約150港紙內<br />\n講下背景資料先： 小弟人在外國，我個層12女4男； 除左兩個香港人，全部當地人，年齡介乎17至22歲。全部好好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我下年會搬出去住，都想留個好印象比佢地。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家覺得啱用，歡迎攞去用。祝大家有個快樂聖誕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2504a76a96aeaeb0947c9b157f3198501411f320","tid":866454,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"Jo Malone 香水"},{"pid":"2274342549cfb3a59fec9210764f168ab68e72e5","tid":866454,"uid":155346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2504a76a96aeaeb0947c9b157f3198501411f320","tid":866454,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"Jo Malone 香水"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"150港紙喎 唔係1500喎。 不過其實如果大家有好提議 貴少少都無所謂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a314261e8a5648bad163b386a97e5bbeff5d4772","tid":866454,"uid":217127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2274342549cfb3a59fec9210764f168ab68e72e5","tid":866454,"uid":155346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"